Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.67,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(888,609)}{\fad(300,300)}第 9 话  『 必定改变未来』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:00.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}占卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还顺便卖炒面面包 形迹可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}潮君 你先来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欢迎来到占卜屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}搞什么 这不是山田嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在下并非山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在下的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宇宙的预言者龙田山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是山田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请叫在下田山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么现在就开始预知你的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请先闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我数到三 不能睁眼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}三 二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你你你你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你刚亲我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你和小田切宁宁在间接接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在使用猿岛的未来预知能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山田的炒面面包卖不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是无奈之举啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过想法是我提的就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们走吧潮君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我已经不要了给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}间接接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在等候时间是40分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}排好队 请排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要保持好队形哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了 我的能力用上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}托你的福炒面面包都卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样算是稍微能还你火灾时的恩情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没什么的 那件事也不至于还要你报答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么山田君 我有些事想找你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个 能够把我魔女的能力抹消吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一接吻就能看见未来什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就不能和喜欢的人交往了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是你吧 叫玉木真一的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又有啰嗦的笨蛋跑来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}找我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是有点突然 但是我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有个魔女希望你能帮她消除能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你到底在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}装傻也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么你知道呢 我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我可是有特别的情报网的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大概也就是泷川诺亚那家伙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说从刚才开始你内心的吐槽 都不小心说出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看来也找不到什么借口了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那你跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就如你所知我的能力就是夺取魔女的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是说我现在就拥有从某个魔女那夺来的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我现在就让你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都说了 你的内心都听到了喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}骗子！变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我所有的能力是让接吻的对象看不见我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是变成透明人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果和其他的魔女接吻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个能力会被替换而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我不能答应你的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下 我也不可能就这么回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是吵死了 既然如此的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜拜 山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样在你面前我应该就消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我说了等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么你还看得见我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总之看起来你是逃不出我的手掌心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:07:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是说你也是类似的魔女杀手咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}魔女…杀手？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你能接受我的请求的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就回应你的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哈？为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交换条件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也可以说是交易
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就暂时先听听好了 说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其实我看中了下任学生会会长的席位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想让你调查一下下届会长的继任者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}继任者？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种事你自己调查不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这可是机密事项
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是轻易就能知道的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山崎确实是守口如瓶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你顺利调查到了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就帮你消除你那位魔女的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}您有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要找会长的话 他在巡视文化祭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}马上就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}久等了久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好意思啊山田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我有点玩过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么你找我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我有话想单独和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 飞鸟的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有作为秘书的她的话 我也当不了会长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们是无法分开的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还是说有女孩子在你会害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是 那我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你准备让谁成为下届学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下届的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对 除了宫村和小田切还有其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你决定是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算是山田你的请求 我也无法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是说你不能告诉我咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可恶 果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要 我拒绝 把我的能力用在这种事情上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话虽这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也很在意会长的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然猿岛有麻烦的话 我也想帮她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的 就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要上了 使用小田切的魅惑能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看 UFO！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}会长 您没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么 你能告诉我为什么你要和我接吻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这可不好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谁要管你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不不 不是我 是山田你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看吧 接下来真的要断了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有什么关系 有一个想消除掉自己能力的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了那个家伙我需要情报啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 我可不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果是这件事的话我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是我请会长帮我消除的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}魔女的透明人的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}透明人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是说玉木的能力是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是我拥有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也认识玉木吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山田你真是让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算是飞鸟的请求也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为还不能做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原本最有竞争力的是玉木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是由于这件事 我不得不重新考虑一下他的评价了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是说三人的评价完全打平了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这可麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算你这么说这也不是能轻易决定的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对了 用比赛来决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这不是轻易地决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你知道吗 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这个学校存在着七位魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说是要找第七个魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}的确至今能确认的魔女有六位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那你们两个事怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是说不算男生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:12:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是只要找到第七个人就能当下届学生会长了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还真是简单明了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们快开始寻找魔女吧 潮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们超研部也开始找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 宫村当不当会长是你的事 跟我们没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是玉木 你可要遵守约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在快把猿岛的能力消除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在还做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你想想 如果我夺取了猿岛的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我所有的透明人的能力就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后就会诞生新的拥有这个能力的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是存在两个迷之魔女游戏就无法成立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别担心啦 我一定会遵守约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这是在找到最后一位魔女之后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是这样 你再等等没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没问题 谢谢你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你跟我接吻就又…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我好像又看到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}讨厌 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太棒了 山田 能力真的消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你 玉木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没什么 这都是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}多亏了这个我才成为了学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看到了怎么样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是你能力消失的未来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再见 我要回活动室了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}OK see you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好 是会议的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看 我的秘书来接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了 山田 这么慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宫村 我们马上去找魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了 跟刚才的态度完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 山田 你看到了怎样的未来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没 没看到什么未来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}撒谎 你见过猿岛之后样子就很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说吧 不说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道了 当上会长的是玉木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这算不上答案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想知道你决定帮助我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你真正看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}白石成为了他的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么啊 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}学生会长的秘书什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不就是年级第一的优等生应有的地位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还是说白石离开了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都说了不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}白石她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真抱歉 让你特地来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天的议题是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是关于演艺部的预算申请和校内展示板的使用规则
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看到她那种表情 我怎么能坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你…难道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 我喜欢白石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些是在学校内惹过事的学生名单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不管魔女愿意或是不愿意 都很容易成为骚动的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}首先从这一点下手比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}昨天的后夜祭你们也没来 还以为你们消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玉木会长的未来有这么不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下 我觉得可以先从这个名单上排除男生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对啊 魔女应该是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不愧是白石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然我想这样说 马上开始调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是在不知道她有什么能力的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请大家谨慎行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}伊藤 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这次的会长选战 请帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这不仅是为了我 也是为了山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有点恶心的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还是什么都没打听出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}山田找魔女有什么理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一定有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在不说可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过 到了可以说的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要原原本本地告诉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你还真是悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还是说你已经放弃当会长了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我只是在等待时机而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是不知道他在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玉木已经没有竞争力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在就是你我二人的竞争了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那家伙还真的特意去挖苦玉木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后还向我汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是太闲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反正我们也没有把玉木放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 我们的目标只是问题学生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你怎么了 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}玉木那家伙 原来打的是那个算盘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们真是太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}听好了 你们三人都中了玉木透明人的计了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}与我最后接吻的是猿岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可是却没有看到你们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是说你们身上有其他人的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}难道说玉木那家伙 潜入过社团活动室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有这个可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然想抢我们的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然这样就赶紧解除掉 破坏那家伙的奸计
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 就这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用身体交换的能力 让玉木的内心改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的 没有人注意到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即使在社团活动室里也可以交换的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是 但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那可是在大家的面前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快点交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那之前我先确认一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你真的愿意交换吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}愿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么愿意 一旦交换 直到未来改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可是都换不回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说不定要有两三天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你说的 我早就做好准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说 说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有件事 关于我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妹妹巽美和老妈会来缠着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你适时敷衍或者无视掉就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 我应付的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有壁橱里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有个写着秘的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 山田同学 怎么还不吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 等下 我还有事要确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你做什么 我还没做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们回部室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等下 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有件事现在要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我看到的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不只是玉木会当上会长…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还看到了你会成为玉木的秘书的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗 那没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}秘书而已 用学习和社团以外的时间去做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我看到 未来的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是第一次和我交换身体时候的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我可是 再也不想看到你那种表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗 是这么回事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过你想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为我不打算再变回原来的自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以拜托了 一定要改变未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}帮我占卜一下能不能交到朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就让龙田山帮你看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下集 山田君与七魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:23:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}影像太模糊了 什么都看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}简直就像透明人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
