Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:40.60,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}如此不同的我们 应该不会错过彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.40,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}对你说着 不要哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.03,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}秘密的约定 无法消失的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.15,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}若能说出 守护你 的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:57.49,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}一定会更轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:01.33,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}但是 已经没有任何办法了
